CUSTOMIZE BOOTSTRAP GRID 


1. cd to bower_components and git clone bootstrap repository


		– git clone https://github.com/twbs/bootstrap.git 

2. cd to bower_components/bootstrap and npm install   


3. open bower_components/bootstrap/less/bootstrap.less and comment unnecesary dependencies */
		
		– needed dependencies*/

		– @import "variables.less"; @import "mixins.less"; @import "grid.less"; @import "media.less"; @import "responsive-utilities.less"; @import "utilities.less";



4. Customize Bootstrap. If bootstrap grid default classes are not wanted.
		– http://stackoverflow.com/questions/18854927/using-mixins-in-bootstrap-3-to-avoid-unsemantic-markup-for-layout-structure


		– override bootstrap default in bootstrap/less/grid.less and bootstrap/less/variables.less was modified to add col-xs 
		

				i. variables.less around line 313  == Container sizes 

				 Added: 
				 @container-phone:             ((420px + @grid-gutter-width)); 
				 @container-xs:                 @container-phone; 

				 grid.less 

				ii. line 28

				 @media (min-width: @screen-xs-min) {
		    		width: @container-xs;
		  		 }
		  		

  				iii. line 83

				 @media (min-width: @screen-xs-min) {
				  .make-grid(xs);
				 }
				

				iv. in less/mixins/grid-framework.less line 21 // Inner gutter via padding

		
			    //padding-left:  (@grid-gutter-width / 2);
		        //padding-right: (@grid-gutter-width / 2);
		        padding-right: 0;
		        padding-left: 0;

		
				v. in less/mixins/grid.less line 9 // container-fixed

		
			  	//padding-left:  (@gutter / 2);
			  	//padding-right: (@gutter / 2);
			  	padding-right: 0;
			  	padding-left: 0;

		
				vi. in less/grid.less line 9 // container-fixed

		
			    .module-wrapper {

		        .container-fixed();
		  		padding-left: 15px;
		  		padding-right: 15px;
				
				}

				.module-fluid {
		        .container-fixed();
				}

				vii. Custom classes are:

				.module-wrapper (15px. padding)
				.module-fluid (0px. padding)


				.module inner (centered + breakpoints)

		



5. from bower_components/bootstrap do grunt dist and copy bower_components/bootstrap/bootstrap.css below 


6. Modified generated css (TODO: find a way to generate from less)


		– Provisionally 
		
				i. @media (min-width: 320px) and (max-width: 479px ) {
				     .module-inner {
				     min-width: 300px;
				     width:90%;
				     }
				    }

				ii. @media (min-width: 480px) and (max-width: 767px ) {
				     .module-inner {
				     min-width: 450px;
				     width:90%;
				     }
				    }
				

				
				iii. .row{margin-left:0; margin-right:0;}
				

				
				iv. added lines 108 to 256


7. Copy paste on partial/_grid.scss
		




